{
  "stem": "4345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my brother-- and Mommy looks at this child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she-- and I see that her eyes well up with tears.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says to him, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nahman, ?] [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't come and ask me any questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do what you want.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She could not see the children be hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we have no food anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- but he didn't go get it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was, at this point, he was eight or going to be eight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just a little baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then slowly but surely, once we knew-- we knew that school was no longer for us, they did not look at us, the non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew already, you know, I-- I just started sensing that something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We started digging ditches in the backyard, by us-- in the garden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did, as children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were given shovels, for our lives, because everybody was glued to the-- we did not own a radio.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were people who could afford it so they owned the radios.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could hear the news coming over the radio that the German army is invading Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mom, you know, and my dad lived through a war, you know, in the 1917 war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knew what war can do to people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Mommy always told us, children, whatever will happen, you try to make it to a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you should be taken away from Dad and I, remember go work in a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You'll have plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look how my mother were-- how my mommy's mind worked-- already worked then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they should take us from her, we should go and-- and work in a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
